  "content_markdown": "Version: 8.3Sales Enterprise\nOn this page\nSet up opportunity stages in the **Opportunity stages** lookup. You can configure the following features:\n* the general list of all available opportunity stages\n* whether to display the stage in the sales pipeline\n* stage sequence in the sales pipeline\nThe setup procedure is as follows:\n1. Click ![icn_system_designer.png](https://academy.creatio.com/docs/sites/en/files/images/Composable_apps/Lead_And_Opportunity_Management/set_up_opportunity_stages/icn_system_designer.png) to **open** the System Designer.\n2. **Go to** the \"System setup\" block \u2192 **Lookups**.\n3. **Open** the \"Opportunities\" lookup folder \u2192 **Opportunity stages** lookup.\n4. **Edit** the stage settings according to your business goals. You can use the editable list or click ![btn_edit.png](https://academy.creatio.com/docs/sites/en/files/images/Composable_apps/Lead_And_Opportunity_Management/set_up_opportunity_stages/btn_edit.png) to open the stage page. View the detailed descriptions of stage settings in the table below.\nName| Description  \n---|---  \nNumber| Define the sequence of stages in the sales pipeline. The column is hidden out of the box. You can add it manually. Learn more: [Set up columns](https://academy.creatio.com/documents?id=1016#title-756-6).  \nDescription| Elaborate when to transfer the opportunity to the next stage. The column is hidden out of the box. You can add it manually. You can add it manually. Learn more: [Set up columns](https://academy.creatio.com/documents?id=1016#title-756-6).  \nFinal| Select the checkbox if the stage is the last stage of the opportunity.  \nSuccessful| Select the checkbox for final stages of won opportunities. The field is non-editable if the **Final** checkbox is cleared.  \nShow in funnel| Select the checkbox to display the stage in the Sales Pipeline dashboard. Learn more: [Sales pipeline](https://academy.creatio.com/documents?id=1572).  \nShow in progress bar| Select the checkbox to display the stage in the progress bar on the opportunity page. The column is hidden out of the box. You can add it manually. Learn more: [Set up columns](https://academy.creatio.com/documents?id=1016#title-756-6).  \n* * *\n## See also\u200b\n[Corporate sale process](https://academy.creatio.com/documents?id=1208)\n[Opportunities FAQ](https://academy.creatio.com/documents?id=1573)",
